I am having touch issues only with my Zenfone 3 (Android). I tested the same code into a Moto G, Moto E and everything is fine.

#### Issue details
When I touch the screen, the method touchDown is called but soon after that the method touchDragged is always called even with just a fast touch.

I solved this comparing both timestamps and ignoring if the differece between both timestamps is too short (less than 100ms).

I am openning this issues to confirm if it happens with other devices.

